<title type="html"><![CDATA[mmc1 powerup and reset]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=1883&amp;p=16140#p16140"><![CDATA[
In some MMC1 tests I did a while back, I made these two notes:<br /><br />- Writing $80 sets bits 2 and 3 of register 0, but doesn't affect anything else.<br /><br />- At power-up, register 0 = $0F and the rest have random values (usually $1F).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Fri Aug 11, 2006 6:34 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
